reviews: Claimed to be compatible with BROTHER MFC-J690DW, however upon installation the printer automatically detects it as "Non-Brother supply" and does not print. Upon restarting the printer, it prints out some sample text but does not print anything I send to the printer.

Love the packaging it came in, was looking for a lighter and less bulky portable charger and I got what I was looking for. Rectangular slim design allows for you to hold your phone and the charger together as one portable package.
Used to always just carry around my cards, this was a life changer.
Came quick and works as advertised, absorbs fairly quickly.
